# 5. Stack Memory in Recursion

Recursion uses the Call Stack.

Example:

```java
fun(3);
```

Stack:

```
Top
-------
fun(0)
fun(1)
fun(2)
fun(3)
-------
Bottom
```

After reaching base case:

```
fun(0) removed
fun(1) removed
fun(2) removed
fun(3) removed
```

This process is called:

### Stack Unwinding

