# 20. Time Complexity Patterns

| Recursion Type | Complexity |
|---------------|------------|
| One recursive call | O(n) |
| Fibonacci recursion | O(2ⁿ) |
| Binary Search recursion | O(log n) |
| Merge Sort recursion | O(n log n) |
| Tower of Hanoi | O(2ⁿ) |

