# 24. Golden Rules of Recursion

✅ Every recursion needs a Base Case

✅ Move toward the Base Case

✅ Smaller problem in each call

✅ Think in terms of function faith

✅ Draw recursion trees for understanding

✅ Watch stack growth

✅ Dry run before coding

